hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 核心寿命：
   $$\tau_H=\frac{E_H\,X\,M_c}{L_H},\qquad \tau_{He}=\frac{E_{He}\,M_c}{L_{He}}.$$ 
2. 使用 $\eta=E_{He}/E_H$ 和 $L\propto\mu^4M^3$ 得出比率：
   $$\frac{\tau_{He}}{\tau_H}
     =\frac{E_{He}/E_H}{X}\frac{L_H}{L_{He}}
     =\frac{\eta}{X}\Bigl(\frac{\mu_H}{\mu_{He}}\Bigr)^4.$$
3. 对于完全电离气体，$Z=1-X-Y$ 时的平均分子量：
   $$\frac1{\mu_H}=2X+\tfrac34Y+\tfrac12Z
     =\tfrac32X+\tfrac14Y+\tfrac12,$$
   $$\frac1{\mu_{He}}=2\cdot0+\tfrac34(X+Y)+\tfrac12Z
     =\tfrac14(X+Y)+\tfrac12.$$
4. 构成比率 $\mu_H/\mu_{He}$：
   $$\frac{\mu_H}{\mu_{He}}
     =\frac{1/(\tfrac32X+\tfrac14Y+\tfrac12)}{1/(\tfrac14(X+Y)+\tfrac12)}
     =\frac{\tfrac14(X+Y)+\tfrac12}{\tfrac32X+\tfrac14Y+\tfrac12}
     =\frac{X+Y+2}{6X+Y+2}.$$
5. 因此
   $$\frac{\tau_{He}}{\tau_H}
     =\frac{\eta}{X}\Bigl(\frac{X+Y+2}{6X+Y+2}\Bigr)^4.$$
